      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior entirely devoid of discernible wear. Meticulously maintained and curated for the most discerning enthusiast, it serves as the definitive benchmark for its class. This offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard market inventory, delivering an experience synonymous with its original delivery state.",
