    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. I\u2019d love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
