    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Can't wait for you to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43900.0,
