    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, WPC-treated rod bearing replacement, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit longitudinal traction. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec bushings and dampening. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original deep luster with zero panel misalignment or oxidative wear. This is a turn-key, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
